replies.body:
As a sona main with over 100  ranked games played and a win rate 70 % diamond 5 (i know dia 5 isnt a high rank but it is 2 me ) i can confirm you are right i wouldn't have made it this far with her if all i know was to smash buttons.
Makes me sad that some people wants her removed. ;(
 {{sticker:sona-playing}}

her design as it stands has some significant overlap with Nami's design and Sona herself is so versatile that the only way to give her weakness is by obliterating her base stats and giving her obnoxious mana cost to limit her ability to spam without forcing her to solve it first with {{item:3070}} .

I want Riot to rework Sona into being a support with specific synergies with high magic damage allies. I feel like a lot of supports have been created to cater to Marksmen and few have been created to cater to other classes in the game. Just Recently we got the Taric rework which has pretty good synergies with melee champions but this is really only one example I can think of.

I think a support that amplifies the magical damage of allies would be a cool niche for her and she would still be great paired with champions like {{champion:110}} {{champion:42}} {{champion:96}} {{champion:115}}
